headline: JPMorgan Upgrades Waste Management (WM) to Overweight, Lifts PT
summary: On Friday, JPMorgan analyst Tami Zakaria upgraded the rating for Waste Management Inc. (NYSE:WM) from Neutral to Overweight, while also raising the price target to $277 from $225. This upgrade follows Zakaria’s initiation of coverage for the waste services sector.
